WebService-Plex

Perl interface to the Plex Media Server API.

This repository is scaffolded as a CPAN-style distribution.
The API surface, tests, metadata, and release notes are expected to evolve.

Current layout:

  lib/    Module source
  t/      Distribution tests

Build/install entry point:

  Makefile.PL

Dependency manifest for developers/tools:

  cpanfile